data.description: Seller is offering $3000 use as you choose and up to $1000 towards a Buyer's Choice Home Warranty.! SELLER CLOSING COSTS AND WARRANTY! Spacious 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home featuring a large front porch and fresh upgrades is waiting for its new owners. When you enter, you will find a large formal dining room to welcome family and friends, newly painted tile in the foyer, and a 1/2 bath for first floor convenience. An open style kitchen, laundry room, and great room with a bay-style window, fireplace, and new laminate flooring is perfect for entertaining family and friends. The pet-friendly fenced-in backyard features a deck and storage building, the ideal private atmosphere for nature lovers to enjoy or to relax with fur friends. Upstairs, you will find a master bedroom with a large walk-in closet and master bath featuring a sunken garden tub and separate shower. Large, spacious guest rooms and guest bathroom on the second floor are perfect for those desiring bedrooms on the same floor within close proximity of each other. Schedule your personal showing today. Seller is offering $3000 use as you choose and up to $1000 towards a Buyer's Choice Home Warranty.
